Son ugasio nade „delija“ [VIDEO]
06 Nov 2019, 22:27 by Milos
Trenutni rezultat utakmice četvrtog kola B grupe Lige šampiona Crvena zvezda – Totenhem je 0:3.
I drugi i treći gol za Sparse postigao je Heung Min Son.
Prvi nakon akcije Delea Alija u 57. minutu



Asistent kod drugog gola bio je Debi Rouz u 60. Minutu.

Son shuts off delia hopes [VIDEO]
06 Nov 2019, 21:27 by Milos
The current score of the fourth round of Group B of the Champions League Red Star - Tottenham is 0: 3.
Both Sparse's second and third goals were scored by Heung Min Son.
The first after Dele Ali's action in the 57th minute



Assistant in the second goal was Debbie Rose in the 60th minute.
